    <item>
      <title>Recurrences</title>
      <link>https://aureooms.github.io/math/2017/04/22/recurrences/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Apr 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://aureooms.github.io/math/2017/04/22/recurrences/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;theorem&#34;&gt;Theorem&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let &lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\( a \in \mathbb{N} \)&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\( t &lt; a \in \mathbb{N} \)&lt;/span&gt;, and &lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\( b \in
\mathbb{R}\)&lt;/span&gt;. Defining &lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\( A_t \)&lt;/span&gt; to be some real number and&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\[
A_N = (1 - \frac{a}{N}) A_{N-1} + b, N &gt; t \in \mathbb{N},
\]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\[
A_N = \frac{b}{1+a} (N+1), N \ge a \in \mathbb{N}.
\]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Converging series</title>
      <link>https://aureooms.github.io/math/2017/04/21/converging-series/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Apr 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://aureooms.github.io/math/2017/04/21/converging-series/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Let &lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\(-1 &lt; x &lt; 1\)&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span  class=&#34;math&#34;&gt;\[
